OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,FA strike by junior doctors in Northern
OL,7,FIreland will lead to thousands of
OL,8,Fpatients missing appointments and
OL,9,Fprocedures, Health Minister Robin
OL,10,FSwann has warned.
OL,12,FIn a written statement to the
OL,13,FAssembly, Mr Swann said that
OL,14,Fdisruption caused by the industrial
OL,15,Faction will be "significant" and
OL,16,Fquestioned what the strike could
OL,17,Fachieve.
