OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,FJunior doctors have voted to take part
OL,7,Fin a 24-hour walkout at hospitals
OL,8,Facross Northern Ireland from 8am on
OL,9,FMarch 6 to 8am on March 7 as part of a
OL,10,Fdispute over pay.
OL,12,FIn his statement, Mr Swann updated
OL,13,FMLAs on the current situation
OL,14,Fregarding pay settlements for staff in
OL,15,Fthe health and social care system
OL,16,Ffollowing recent industrial action.
