OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,FUnder a proposed settlement, thousands
OL,7,Fof health workers in the region will
OL,8,Fhave pay parity with England restored
OL,9,Fon their pay bands and will receive an
OL,10,Funconsolidated lump sum for all staff
OL,11,Fon Agenda for Change terms and
OL,12,Fconditions.
OL,14,FThis means workers will receive a
OL,15,Fconsolidated pay uplift of 5% and a
OL,16,Fnon-consolidated (pro-rata) payment of
OL,17,F#1,505.
OL,19,FTrade unions have agreed to ballot
OL,20,Ftheir members on the proposed
OL,21,Fsettlement.
