OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,FMr Swann said: "I want the unions now
OL,7,Fto be given the time and space to hold
OL,8,Fthe ballots.
OL,10,F"The pay offer has been made possible
OL,11,Fthrough additional monies made
OL,12,Favailable by HM Government.
OL,14,F"I know members will share my concern
OL,15,Fat the one-off nature of this funding
OL,16,Fand my hope that additional support
OL,17,Fwill be made available in future
OL,18,Fyears, given the recurrent nature of
OL,19,Fpay settlements."
