OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,FHowever, the minister said progress
OL,7,Fhad not been achieved in relation to
OL,8,Fthe planned industrial action by
OL,9,Fjunior doctors.
OL,11,FHe said: "The BMA junior doctors
OL,12,Fcommittee has repeatedly made clear
OL,13,Fthat it wants my department to go
OL,14,Fbeyond the pay offer made in England,
OL,15,Fas recommended by the DDRB, a national
OL,16,Fpay review body.
