OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,F"For junior doctors, the DDRB
OL,7,Frecommendations offer an average pay
OL,8,Fincrease of 9.1% in 2023/24 with those
OL,9,Fin their first year receiving a 10.7%
OL,10,Fuplift.
OL,12,F"This award will be back-dated and
OL,13,Fpayable to all staff from April 2023.
OL,15,F"This offer should be viewed in the
OL,16,Fcontext of pay settlements across the
OL,17,Fwider Northern Ireland public sector.
