OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,F"This pay uplift will bring junior
OL,7,Fdoctor basic pay here above the level
OL,8,Fin Wales, and closer to the level in
OL,9,FEngland."
OL,11,FMr Swann said he was willing to
OL,12,Fdiscuss contract reform with junior
OL,13,Fdoctors, but added: "I have made clear
OL,14,Fthat there are limits beyond which I
OL,15,Fcannot go in relation to pay offers
OL,16,Fthis year."
