OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,FHe said: "Implementing the
OL,7,Frecommendations of independent pay
OL,8,Freview bodies or mirroring pay
OL,9,Fsettlements in England is the maximum
OL,10,Fthat can be afforded at this juncture.
OL,12,F"This reflects the current and looming
OL,13,Fsevere budgetary pressures on my
OL,14,Fdepartment and across all departments.
OL,16,F"I have appealed to the BMA junior
OL,17,Fdoctors committee to re-consider the
OL,18,Fplanned industrial action and I do so
OL,19,Fagain.
