OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,F"I entirely appreciate the
OL,7,Ffrustrations of their members ` not
OL,8,Fjust on pay but on other pressing
OL,9,Fissues including health service
OL,10,Fpressures and working conditions."
OL,12,FHe continued: "The demand that below-
OL,13,Finflation pay increases over the past
OL,14,Fdecade be remedied is beyond the reach
OL,15,Fof the NI Executive and Assembly.
OL,17,F"This is a national issue, reflecting
OL,18,Fnational government policy, and has
OL,19,Fimpacted on public sector workforces
OL,20,Facross the UK.
