OL,3,CJunior doctors' strike 'will lead to
OL,4,Cthousands of missed appointments'
OL,6,F"If there is a solution, it will be a
OL,7,Fnational one. I would, therefore,
OL,8,Fquestion what industrial action in a
OL,9,FNI context can hope to achieve.
OL,11,F"As Health Minister, I also have to
OL,12,Fplace on record my deep concern over
OL,13,Fthe implications for patient care.
OL,15,F"HSC Trust will of course do all they
OL,16,Fcan to mitigate impacts
OL,18,F"At this point, it is anticipated that
OL,19,Fdisruption will be significant with
OL,20,Fthousands of patients missing out on
OL,21,Fappointments and procedures.
